Chat Page UI

A simple chat interface web page built using HTML and CSS, showcasing a conversation between two people. The project focuses on designing a clean, responsive chat layout with styled messages for sent and received texts.

Features

Realistic chat interface layout.

Different styling for sent and received messages.

Background image for enhanced visual appeal.

Easy to customize for any conversation.

Technologies Used

HTML – Structure of the chat page.

CSS – Styling messages, background, and layout.
